text: Neudeck may refer to: *the former estate of Paul von Hindenburg, today Ogrodzieniec, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, a village in northern Poland * the former estate of Guido Henckel von Donnersmarck (1830–1916), today Świerklaniec in Upper Silesia *Neudeck in the suburbs of Munich ==People== *Rupert Neudeck, German humanitarian *Ruth Neudeck, German SS supervisor at death camps and war criminal
title: Neudeck
